1. Get the input from the user.

    'арбидол'

2. Get the alphabet characters list.
 
    [{'key': 'А', 'value': '//www.rlsnet.ru/tn_alf_letter_c0.htm'},{...},{...},{...}]
     
3. Get the link to a particular character page.
    
    "https:"  + "//www.rlsnet.ru/tn_alf_letter_c0.htm"

4. Get the medicament list from that particular character page.

    [{'key': 'Арбидол® (Arbidol)', 'value': '//www.rlsnet.ru/tn_index_id_4196.htm'},{...},{...},{...}]

5. Find the inputted medicament in the medicament list.
    
    'арбидол' == 'Арбидол® (Arbidol)'
    
6. If there is more than one search results, go to choose-template.        
    
7. Go the medicament page and search a combination of words "клинические исследования".

